the <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.scottishsocialistparty.org" target="top">Scottish Socialist Party</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> manifesto includes:<br>
 - minimum wages for public sector workers raised from £3.60(18-20) or £4.20 (over 21s) per hour, to £7.32 per hour for 16+<br>
 - council tax abolished, in favour of fairer system, based on income<br>
 - improved rights for women<br>
 - improved rights for homosexuals<br>
 - improved rights for youths<br>
 - improved rights for the elderly(including an increase in state pensions, free public transport travel, free tv lincenses and free heating fuel between october and april)<br>
 - improved rights for the disabled<br>
 - action against crime<br>
 - action against sectarianism<br>
 - action against racism<br>
 - action on health, transport, rural decline, fishing, the environment, education and housing.<br>
and much more<br>
